model_explanation: "only gave SUE apples" means Sue only received apples, and not other fruits from Sam. S2 talks about bananas, which isn't entailed or contradicted directly by S1. So they are independent.
"only gave ELLEN oranges" means Ellen is the only person who got oranges from Sam. S2 discusses what Tom didn't get, which is independent of the focused assertion about Ellen.
"only gave TOM apples" entails that no one else, including Mary, received apples from Sam. Therefore, S2 is entailed by S1.

"only gave BILL grapes" means Bill is the only person who got grapes. Therefore, S2 is entailed because Sue didn’t get any grapes.
